Package: qsip
Type: Package
Title: Quantitative stable isotope probing for microbial ecology
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
  person('Bram', 'Stone', email='stone.bram@gmail.com', role=c('cre','aut')),
  person('Ben', 'Koch', role='aut'),
  person('Bruce', 'Hungate', role='aut'))
Maintainer: Bram Stone <stone.bram@gmail.com>
Description: This package contains code that allows for the 
    quantification of fractional istope enrichment for each individual 
    microbial taxon in a microbial community. Data on isotope 
    enrichment are paired with taxon-specific relative abundances
    and absolute abundances and can be used to determine taxon-specific growth 
    and death rates for population-level modeling.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    data.table (>= 1.14.6)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
